synopsis:
D’ART Shtajio teamed up with Spiff TV to produce an anime Music Video – Thinkin ft. Anuel AA, Bad Bunny, Future. ‘Thinkin’ Directed by D’ART Shtajio CEO Arthell Isom and Spiff TV, the animated music video follows the story of ‘The Union’ recapping the crazy night they had before with things getting very out of hand.

(Source: Official Website)
